Package gw.api.webservice.messagingTools

Class MessageStatisticsData

java.lang.Object
gw.api.webservice.messagingTools.MessageStatisticsData
All Implemented Interfaces:
GWRemotable
public final class MessageStatisticsData extends Object implements GWRemotable
Holds the statistics for messages for a given safe ordered object. The statistics include:
  • # of failed messages
  • # of failed messages that can be retried
  • # of inflight messages
  • # of unsent messages
